            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ce canahya tlen cihuameh, tlen quimanextia ica campa axneci ica occiental ica campa Cihuateteoh quihuicah tonatiuh quemman motlalia pan Mictlan (tlalli tlen mictoqueh).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
